| 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)
|
|diff --git a/_global/extensions/openspec-gates.ts b/_global/extensions/openspec-gates.ts
|index ee2529e..8cafc48 100644
|--- a/_global/extensions/openspec-gates.ts
|+++ b/_global/extensions/openspec-gates.ts
|@@ -82,6 +82,8 @@ Check:
| - Evidence: cite concrete file paths, task text, requirement IDs, or diff/spec text only.
| - Blockers: missing scope, constraints, traceability, verification, or archive/sync work.
| - Napkin: use as prior memory; call out conflicts instead of letting it override artifacts.
|+- Oracle checkpoints: when stage readiness depends on unavailable or ambiguous review-critical evidence, require a repo-local checkpoint that records question, inspected evidence, decision, owner, and next action. If no checkpoint exists, emit a finding that says missing oracle checkpoint, route=human, promoted=yes.
|+- Concrete blockers: if the artifact reports a specific blocker and does not claim the stage is complete, accept that stop condition instead of demanding an oracle checkpoint.
|
| Finding tags: every finding uses severity plus class, scope, route, and promoted tags. Prefer class=omission|systematic|incoherent|preference|env|pattern, scope=proposal|spec|design|tasks|review|tooling, route=auto-fix|prompt|deterministic-check|spec-rule|human|guidance.
